# Regenerate with: vhs docs/demo.tape   (from the repo root, after
# building: cmake --build build-rel -j, so the "first run" build step
# doesn't appear in the recording).
Output docs/demo.gif
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 1000
Set Height 620
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 30ms

Type "./run-demo.sh"
Enter
Sleep 18s
Ctrl+C
Sleep 1s
